CustomField.description: Fee percentage by which to increase the billable amount of the Expense, defaulted from the Project. 0% means no increase (default), whereas 100% means double. The calculation will apply the percentage expense fee*before* any flat expense fee.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Fee percentage by which to increase the billable amount of the Expense, defaulted from the Project. 0% means no increase (default), whereas 100% means double. The calculation will apply the percentage expense fee*before* any flat expense fee.
CustomField.label: Billable Fee Percentage
